What you need to know:  Rio is competing in the Equator Rally in a Ford Fiesta F2 category, the only two-wheel-drive car after Leonardo Varese in a Toyota Vitz, in the main ARC eventHis aim is a class victory which will put him in better stead to proceed to Europe to compete in the European ChampionshipVeteran Ian Duncan in a classic Nissan 240RS may not be the fastest but certainly not the slowest